{"tid":1114104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊扮柯P行竊 磁吸娃娃機台3秒得手","createTime":"2019-04-18T09:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T09:50:23.000Z","uid":55792,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22787179fb32bf812b0aa0908b500d4f69b3ecad","tid":1114104,"uid":55792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190417/1424091.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190417%2F1424091.htm&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dPsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=4e8893a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190417/1424091.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n台北市長柯文哲人氣爆紅，網路上更可看到其仰天長笑的或是揪著臉大笑模樣的面具，意外變成年輕人惡搞的手法。16日傳出，台南有一名竊賊戴著柯文哲的面具行竊夾娃娃機，對此，柯文哲被問到此事時先是大笑，接著反問，「娃娃機怎麼偷？直接打破去偷是不是？」，並直言這實在太有趣了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtx3czb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdtx3czb.png&h=9942210f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QFcQkT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QFcQkT.png&h=646cde47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133b44c1849461efbcbaad3ae4ab35adb9956f86","tid":1114104,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"個面具好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a1b2adfb07abdf04aff71ebf6a6897947b46a1","tid":1114104,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"係咪郭子乾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}